---

# iota 🔥🔥🔥 (VERY IMPORTANT)

Auto incrementing constants.

---

# Example

```go id="wfdmto"
const (
    Sunday = iota
    Monday
    Tuesday
    Wednesday
)
```

---

# Values

```text id="7mbzn0"
Sunday = 0
Monday = 1
Tuesday = 2
Wednesday = 3
```

---

# Real Usage of iota

Used for:

* enums
* states
* statuses

---

# Example

```go id="cq1y6w"
const (
    Pending = iota
    Approved
    Rejected
)
```

---

# Scope in Go 🌍

Scope = variable kaha accessible hai.

---

# Local Scope

Inside function only.

```go id="q5q6q5"
func main() {
    age := 21
}
```

---

# Global Scope

Outside function.

```go id="3h9pme"
var appName = "MyApp"
```

---

# Shadowing ⚠️

Inner variable outer variable ko hide kar deta hai.

---

# Example

```go id="6s57ij"
package main

import "fmt"

var name = "Global"

func main() {

    name := "Local"

    fmt.Println(name)
}
```

Output:

```text id="m5uy38"
Local
```

Local variable ne global ko shadow kar diya.

---

# Full Example 🚀

```go id="wq1bn1"
package main

import "fmt"

const company = "Google"

func main() {

    name := "Sourav"
    var age int = 21

    fmt.Println(name)
    fmt.Println(age)
    fmt.Println(company)
}
```

---

