# Real Backend Example

Suppose database se users aaye:

```go
users := []string{
    "Sourav",
    "Rahul",
    "Aman",
}
```

Add new user:

```go
users = append(users,"Rohit")
```

Easy.

Isi liye slices backend me everywhere use hote hain.

